description:
Bunnie listened to all the women in her DM's, and welcomes the sexy voiced rapper FJ Outlaw to the show this week to talk a little dirty and spill the tea. FJ explains why he's never cheated or had a threesome (yet!), and what he looks for in a hookup. FJ opens up about processing the pain of losing his loved ones and best friends, signing with Mako Music Group, how he got into rap, and why he sleeps fully clothed gripping a pistol. 

"Money reveals character, it doesn't hide it." - Bunnie 

"Good music is good music." - FJ
